inyokaedit (0.7.0-0ubuntu1) precise; urgency=low

  [Dominique Lasserre]
  * No longer needed lintian override removed (spelling Programm - Program).

  [ Thorsten Roth ]
  * Article and article image download via Qt modules.
  * Added progressbar while article image download.
  * Added Ubuntu 12.10 Quantal Quetzal.
  * Code and file reorganization.
  * Added scrollbar features (save position from preview, sychronous scrolling
    of editor and preview).
  * Loading user defined gui language.
  * Insertion of macros via file.
  * Defining templates menu and dropdown menu via XML file.
  * Added new interwiki links and flags.
  * Homogeneous coding style and linting.
  * Some bug fixes (highlighting, infinite loop, monotype, paragraph character).

 -- Dominique Lasserre <lasserre.d@gmail.com>  Sun, 04 Nov 2012 17:16:29 +0100

