inyokaedit (0.4.0-0ubuntu1) precise; urgency=low

  [Dominique Lasserre]
  * Improved Makefile (installation target). Hunspell dependency now optional
    (dynamic check with pkg-config which is a new dependency). Spellchecker can
    be disabled (but is enabled by default). LP: #951056
  * Added me to authors of debian/*.
  * Accept libqt4-dev << 4:4.7.0 as replacement of libqtwebkit-dev.

  [Thorsten Roth]
  * Fixed LP: #941308 (No edit after search), LP: #904439 (Show preview
    alongside editor), LP: #969649 (crash on startup), LP: #889321 and #922808
    (cursor moving and marking issues).
  * Added simple logging function.
  * Added possibility to check interwiki links for validity.

